//-------------------------------------------------------------+
//                                                             +
// Running CAEN digitizers, Save waveform to ROOT file         +
//                                                             +
// Pietro Giampa, RHUL 2013                                    +
//                                                             +
//-------------------------------------------------------------+


This Allows the user to take charge data with a CAEN board,  all the code has been done via the CAENDigitizer
library which it should be compatible with all the CAEN boards.

The Readout from the digitizer is saved into a TTree called "dmtpc" which has :
	- TH1S of the waveform
	- Record Length
	- Event Counter
	- Trigger Time Tag

//-------------------------------------------------------------+

TO COMPILE :

1) Make clean;

2) Make caen;

- This should build an executable "caen" in the main directory


